lead_paragraph: Cal Clutterbuck scored the tiebreaking goal with 1:28 remaining in the third period and the New York Islanders defeated the New York Rangers 6-4 on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Islanders Score 2 Late Goals to Top Rival Rangers 6-4
